{"tid":1436953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[另類文宣] 寫咗封港式Email比機場遊客，求意見","createTime":"2019-08-09T11:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T11:52:34.000Z","uid":36592,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9736bbad8c99e73388e3fa21186add08ea84d088","tid":1436953,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:45:44.000Z","msg":"用字絕對香港風味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/09/i1RnU5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F09%2Fi1RnU5.jpg&h=3b9c2c6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n風格夠柒可以喺其他高質文宣中突圍而出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條片係NY Times既721元朗恐襲調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以印A3 Size做人肉QR Code比旅客scan<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者入落信封當信咁派比佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無必要加埋特首辦同埋盧偉聰電話比旅客查詢香港發生咗咩事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家比d意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bda46dff86b873099223a69d43597fdfc57c7c9","tid":1436953,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:46:29.000Z","msg":"Dear Tourists,<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Re: Your Stay in Hong Kong</strong></div><br />\n<br />\nWelcome to Hong Kong. Please find below a report by the New York Times for your information:<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fDtM3dEJdHo \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfDtM3dEJdHo%20&d=mdS8n1K3gC4RK9SJ0KjOq%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=9278b4df\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fDtM3dEJdHo </a><br />\n<br />\nFor enquiries, you may contact the Hong Kong Police Force and/or the Hong Kong government.<br />\n<br />\nWe wish you a pleasant stay in Hong Kong. Thank you.<br />\n<b